GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_EnterpriseShapePrimaryFocus> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_EnterpriseShapePrimaryFocus> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_EnterpriseShapePrimaryFocus> ;
    narr:childCount "12"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "4ee3dfa1b09322db9414ced26486e26d250bbe96" ;
    narr:narration """The search for a primary sales focus has shifted toward the [enterprise customer-shape](narr:Position_EnterpriseShapeTentativePriority) as a tentative priority, defined not by organizational scale but by a specific [engagement pattern](narr:Position_EnterpriseShapeEngagementPattern) involving internal expertise bottlenecks and stakeholder access. This trajectory is currently gated by [explicit validation criteria](narr:Position_EnterpriseShapeValidationCriteria) to avoid over-indexing on a single pilot, while [expertise-distributor archetypes](narr:Position_ExpertiseDistributorDeprioritized) have been relegated to a secondary track. Recent refinements suggest that the [expert-as-bottleneck](narr:Position_ConvergenceBuyerIsPlural) narrative is more accurately a 'decision junction' story, where the buyer is plural and the core pain is [memory scarcity](narr:Position_SelfIDAsQualifyingSignal). A new, high-conviction [GTM wedge](narr:Narrative_DiscoveryToolGTMWedge) has emerged: positioning the tool as infrastructure for consulting discovery engagements, which offers a sellable focus without [clipping the wings](narr:Narrative_GeneralVsSellableTension) of the broader, general-purpose capability. Qualification is now sharpened by [deployment-specific diagnostics](narr:Position_CohortDiagnosticForProspects) and a [strict disqualification rule](narr:Position_DisqualificationRule) for non-buyers.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DiscoveryToolGTMWedge> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_GeneralVsSellableTension> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_CohortDiagnosticForProspects> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_ConvergenceBuyerIsPlural> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_DisqualificationRule> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_EnterpriseCustomerARBConvergenceSpeed> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_EnterpriseShapeEngagementPattern> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_EnterpriseShapeTentativePriority> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_EnterpriseShapeValidationCriteria> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_ExpertiseDistributorDeprioritized> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_SelfIDAsQualifyingSignal> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_SponsorNotChampionYouAreChampion> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "the bottleneck is not scarce expertise but scarce memory at the decision junction" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_ConvergenceBuyerIsPlural> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "aswritten as the infrastructure for consulting discovery engagements" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DiscoveryToolGTMWedge> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "a sponsor is excited and aligned; a champion rams it through internally" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_SponsorNotChampionYouAreChampion> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "no answers to questions two and three means friendly or pass, not buyer" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_DisqualificationRule> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "you've got to package it in different wrapping paper for different industries" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_GeneralVsSellableTension> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The 'discovery tool' wedge provides a concrete sellable use case, but risks narrowing the product's general-purpose moat." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DiscoveryToolGTMWedge> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_GeneralVsSellableTension> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The enterprise-shape focus remains tentative and potentially rationalized by a sample-of-one pilot." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_EnterpriseShapeTentativePriority> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_EnterpriseCustomerARBConvergenceSpeed> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The lack of an internal champion means the vendor must act as the project manager, or the deal risks stalling." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_SponsorNotChampionYouAreChampion> ] ;
    narr:writer "google/gemini-3.1-flash-lite" .
